Date: 1997-01-08

Title: Relations between correlators in gauge field theory

Authors: V.I. Shevchenko and Yu.A. Simonov

Comments: 11 pages, LaTeX

Journal-ref: Phys.Atom.Nucl. 60 (1997) 1201-1205; Yad.Fiz. 60N7 (1997)

1329-1333Exact relations between gauge-invariant vacuum correlators in QCD arederived. Derivatives of the correlators are expressed in terms of higher orderscorrelators. The behaviour of the correlators at large and small distances dueto these relations is discussed.